summary: A spelltome that conjures the Death Overlord. I finally did it!
descriptionHtml:
After many hours on the CK, I finally figured how to add a new character to the spelltome so I can conjure him. The possibilities are great. Now I am able to make mods that the player can conjure, say a giant mud crab, the giant himself, werewolfs, saber cat, a character you made and wish him or her conjurable. 
This mod, I made the death overlord as a trying element, I made him much taller and now he retains duration time of 60 seconds as per usual. I hope you guys like this spell. 

Where to get it
Go to Riverwood Traders, it\'s in one of the chest on the second level. (sorry I forgot to include this text)
author: simplesim
